        <content><![CDATA[<p>To add a new resource type, click the add wizard in the toolbar (<img style="width: 14px;" title="searchBigIconActive" src="%(link0)" alt="" />). A dialog pops up, where you can configure the new type.</p>
<p>In a first step, you choose the module, the type should be part of. Therefor, you get a list of the currently installed modules. Select the one, you want to add the resource type to and click "OK".</p>
<p>Next, a dialog is shown where you can configure the type:</p>]]></content>
